description:
Browse the web
  • Wide collection of addons, including ad blockers.
  • Improved tracking protection.
  • Private mode available in a single tap.
  • Customizable start screen layout and navigation bar position (top or bottom).
  • Dark theme.
  • Collections of tabs.
  • Synchronization of tabs, bookmarks, passwords, etc. across multiple devices via Firefox Sync.
  • Picture-in-picture mode.

Fennec F-Droid is based on the latest Mozilla Firefox release. It has proprietary bits and telemetry removed, but still connects to various Mozilla services that can track users.
